%U A391418 1,1,2,2,1,1,1,1,1,1,1,2,1,1,2,1,1,2
%N A391418 Class number of order of real quadratic fields with discriminant D = A079896(n).
%C A391418 In other words, number of classes in the form class group quotient by {I,-I} of discriminant D, where I is the principal class. (So I corresponds to the form x^2 - (D/4)*y^2 for 4|D and x^2 - x*y - ((D-1)/4)*y^2 for D == 1 (mod 4), and -I corresponds to the form (D/4)*x^2 - y^2 for 4|D and ((D-1)/4)*x^2 - x*y - y^2 for D == 1 (mod 4)).
%H A391418 Jianing Song, <a href="/A391418/b391418.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%o A391418 (PARI) for(n=2, 200, if(n%4 <= 1 && !issquare(n), print1(qfbclassno(n), ", ")))
%Y A391418 For a list of sequences related to the class numbers of real quadratic fields, see A087048.
%K A391418 nonn,changed
%O A391418 1,14
%A A391418 _Jianing Song_, Dec 09 2025
